infoTxt: • Any discrepancy in the statement should be brought to the notice of YES BANK LIMITED within one month from the date of the statement.
The SMS alert facility for debits to your demat A/C has now been enhanced by NSDL.
In case of delivery instructions effected up to 7.00 p.m.,you will receive SMS alerts on the same day.

In case of delivery instructions effected after 7.00 p.m.,you will receive SMS alerts on the following day. Please visit www.nsdl.co.in, for the terms and conditions applicable to the SMS alert facility.
Please submit the Nomination declaration for your Demat A/C by November 30, 2011, at your nearest YES BANK branch.
You can now hold your Mutual Fund investments as well in your YES BANK Demat A/C. For more information, please contact your Depository Participant or your Stock Broker.

In the event of closing or shifting of the demat account from YES Bank to another participant, the AMC collected upfront on annual basis by YES Bank, will be refunded to the customer for the balance quarter/s, provided the account is not being closed / shifted in the last quarter, since recovery.
Please register your mobile number & email addresses with YES BANK and also regularly update the same in order to receive communication from Companies.

wealthPage.infoTxt1:
The information relating to mutual fund holdings and transactions have been taken from the R & T Agents of AMCs. However, these may not necessarily be the "available balance" in the account. Please ask your Relationship Manager to confirm your available balance prior to placing/executing the order.If any
changes are required for the above information due to sale/purchase/redemption, please inform us in writing to enable us to update your records. Initial cost of holding is calculated on first-in-first-out (FIFO) basis. Yes Bank Ltd. does not guarantee the accuracy or completeness of the information. You should
independently verify the information before making any investment decision or for any tax/legal /regulatory reporting.In case of any discrepancies, please bring these to notice of your relationship manager. This statement is for information purpose only and should not be regarded as offer to sell, or a solicitation of an offer to purchase or subscribe for any investment. Mutual Fund Investments are subject to market risks please read the offer document carefully before investing.

importantMessages: For non-CTS 2010 Standard cheques, separate clearing session has been introduced in Mumbai, Chennai and New Delhi for clearing (including PDC and EMI cheques) and will operate once a week (every Monday) from November 1, 2014 onwards. If the identified day for clearing non-CTS-2010 instruments falls on a holiday under the Negotiable Instruments Act, 1881, presentation session on such occasions will be conducted on the previous working day.

If you receive any e-mail, phone call or voice message, requesting your Netbanking or Debit Card details like PIN, Password, Account number or Debit Card Details, please do not respond to it and inform us at yestouch@yesbank.in or call our toll free number at 18002000.

To avail of exemption from TDS deduction on your Fixed Deposit (FD), please submit Form 15 G/H for each FD or Exemption Certificate issued by Income Tax Department (as applicable) every Financial Year. In accordance with the Income Tax Act, TDS will be deducted at a higher rate of 20% (wherever applicable) for accounts without PAN details. Also, in the absence of PAN details, Form 15G/H & Exemption Certificates will be deemed invalid. To update the PAN details for your account, kindly visit mySPACE on your YES BANK Retail NetBanking or visit your nearest YES BANK branch. Kindly ignore this message if already updated.
YES BANK Raipur branch has been relocated to Golchha Chambers, Civil Lines, Main Road, Sant Kabir Chowk, Near Holy Hearts School, w.e.f. 16 Oct 2014.
